        "subject": "LU-9384 test: Add conf-sanity 32b,c to ALWAYS_EXCEPT",
        "message": "LU-9384 test: Add conf-sanity 32b,c to ALWAYS_EXCEPT\n\nWith recent patch landings to the master branch, conf-sanity\ntests 32b and 32c are failing at a high rate. We need to add\nthese tests to the ALWAYS_EXCEPT list so that they are not\nexecuted until a fix for the underlying issue is found.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial testlist=conf-sanity\nSigned-off-by: James Nunez <james.a.nunez@intel.com>\nChange-Id: Iaa4410166d4baa83ff210e2d8f4fe9ea27a4b487\n"
